cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with detecting fake face images. It may also belong to multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves tampered videos. Additionally, it may fall under the sub-categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR) as it discusses the potential harm of improper use of GANs, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques, and machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a new method for detecting fake images using contrastive loss and a classifier.
